'''Surtsey''' was an island on the [[City/Legends|city]]-[[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] and was the location of [[Mon Mothma/Legends|Mon Mothma's]] estate after her retirement. [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]] visited her there at least twice: once in [[16 ABY/Legends|16 ABY]] and again in [[17 ABY/Legends|17 ABY]].

==Behind the scenes==
[[Wikipedia:Surtsey|Surtsey]] is a volcanic island located off the southern coast of Iceland.

